{"tid":816951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：容海恩農曆新年生B 盼設遙距投票 - 李八方","createTime":"2018-09-13T05:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T08:18:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e781c823cfa0a7adfd04c33a168416b08866ffee","tid":816951,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180913/20498481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F20498481&d=1omiQOYDo2tM%2Bh4nfUKcwv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3f8e12c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180913%2F20498481&h=66be1e5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180913/20498481</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月13日 <br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：容海恩農曆新年生B<br />\n盼設遙距投票 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180913/large/a1105a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180913%2Flarge%2Fa1105a.jpg&h=97871d6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n上月下嫁同黨政策總裁袁彌昌嘅新民黨立法會議員容海恩（圖），一直有傳佢有咗BB，但容海恩始終冇承認又冇否認，到噚晚佢接受Now新聞訪問，終於解開腹中係咪多嚿肉之謎，佢承認已經有咗BB 4個月，預產期係出年二月農曆新年，即係會生個豬BB喎，至於BB係男仔定女仔？恩恩豬話遲啲先透露。八方打畀恩恩豬恭喜佢，佢話 𠵱家有孕吐情況，一早一晚特別唔舒服，多得屋企人照顧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奉子成婚「係個人選擇」<br />\n<br />\n八方睇返訪問片段，今次奉子成婚，實有人閒言閒語，但恩恩豬喺訪問度話結婚完全係個人選擇。恩恩豬話有BB唔會減少參加事務委員會等工作，不過大肚婆要產檢、安胎，佢都話開會投票會有影響，希望立法會可以遙距投票或者建立授權票制度，其實立法會都要與時並進，搞吓媽媽友善環境，而且BB將會係立會第一B，各位議員同事都要幫手爭取啦！  <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：阿鼎：香港是一個國家　網民譏「激進過掟磚」 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：陸頌雄同肥彭合照　惡搞小學雞設計對白 (李八方)"},{"pid":"7a9222319112bdc4bee9998b942e3577ed4e14b4","tid":816951,"uid":205462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"個人選擇嘅話，就唔好自認係耶閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393f060ce963f4e5053a4aed04bf42b20ee6a51e","tid":816951,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"好淫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5320361e7665b7679740a5909a2204c544f2f83a","tid":816951,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"bitch呀哥可以日日屌到水野朝陽 你話幾幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5975f3c9b30445bed3c16085bf770bc1d78a7da","tid":816951,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"立法會議員唔撚開會都照出足糧啦，講產假多撚餘"},{"pid":"d20ae12a491f7ef39d22f19d6eda22243155a7c9","tid":816951,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"又一個未婚懷孕耶人"},{"pid":"293da062fac0894f6b190bcde44cc3c490e5cad4","tid":816951,"uid":81562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:00:55.000Z","msg":"已經想像到楊岳橋抱住佢個B影相個撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209018877e998c8f9331799f98fb36e368ae79b1","tid":816951,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:18:58.000Z","msg":"水野朝陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}